Detailed Description

Container for Sierra spot weld information.

Description:

This struct holds information specific to Sierra spot welds. Indices into the owning FC_SierraInfo struct's function list are also provided for the normal and tangential functions. (E.g. given FC_SierraInfo sierra, the normal function of the ith spotweld can be found as sierra->functions[sierra->spotwelds[i]->normalId].)

Modifications:

  • 2003-JUN-24 W Koegler Created.
  • 2003-SEP-02 W Koegler Added all possible spot weld variables.
  • 2007-OCT-15 ACG removed refs to saf.
